Package: tads
Version: 2.5.6
Revision: 2
Maintainer: Alexander Strange <astrange@ithinksw.com>
Source: http://www.ifarchive.org/if-archive/programming/tads2/source/tads2src-256.tar.gz
SourceDirectory: tads2
GCC: 3.1
PatchScript: sed 's:@PREFIX@:%p:g' <%a/%f.patch | patch -p1
CompileScript: (cd unix; OS_VERS=`uname``uname -r` make) 
InstallScript: <<
 mkdir -p %i/bin
 cp unix/tadsr unix/tadsc unix/tdb %i/bin
 ./unix/tadsc -ds2 testux.t
 ./unix/tadsc -ds2 tests/bugs.t
 mkdir -p %i/include
 cp adv.t std.t %i/include
<<
DocFiles: portnote.txt README readtads.src tests/bugs.t tests/bugs.gam testux* tadserr.msg tadsver.htm unix/tadsver.uni
Description: Interactive fiction runtime + compiler
DescPort: <<
TADS's configuration system is badly done.
The makefile is patched to enable the Darwin rules and to use Fink's ncurses instead of libSystem.
<<
